Title: How Does Quantum Vacuum Energy Accelerate?
Authors: K. A. Milton and P. Parashar and J. Wagner and K. V. Shajesh and A. Romeo and S. Fulling
Abstract: We show that Casimir energy for a configuration of parallel plates gravitates according to the equivalence principle both for the finite and divergent parts. This shows that the latter can be absorbed by a process of renormalization.
